OL,3,CGrant Shapps refuses to commit to 3%
OL,4,Cdefence spending in election manifesto
OL,6,FThe Defence Secretary won't guarantee
OL,7,Fthat the Conservatives will pledge to
OL,8,Fincrease defence spending to 3% in
OL,9,Ftheir election manifesto.
OL,11,FGrant Shapps refused to make the
OL,12,Fcommitment in an interview with ITV
OL,13,FWest Country on Wednesday 10 April,
OL,14,Fdespite calls from senior Tories to do
OL,15,Fso.
OL,17,FMr Shapps recently suggested he would
OL,18,Fsupport a rise to 3% of GDP, telling
OL,19,Freporters in Poland that he wants "a
OL,20,Fbigger budget" and is "clearly in
OL,21,Ffavour" of the target.
