OL,3,CGrant Shapps refuses to commit to 3%
OL,4,Cdefence spending in election manifesto
OL,6,FBut when asked on a visit near Bristol
OL,7,Fwhether he could commit to putting an
OL,8,Fincrease in the Conservatives general
OL,9,Felection manifesto, Mr Shapps said:
OL,10,F"That will be a matter for another
OL,11,Fday."
OL,13,F"What I can tell you, is that the
OL,14,Fgovernment is committed to 2.5%," he
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,17,FMr Shapps met workers at the
OL,18,Fprocurement arm of the Ministry of
OL,19,FDefence in Abbey Wood, near Bristol.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
