OL,3,CGrant Shapps refuses to commit to 3%
OL,4,Cdefence spending in election manifesto
OL,6,FA marginal seat, it is a key Labour
OL,7,Ftarget for the upcoming general
OL,8,Felection.
OL,10,FClaire Hazelgrove, Labour's candidate,
OL,11,Ftold ITV West Country that the Party's
OL,12,Felection manifesto will contain full
OL,13,Fdetails of its policies and costings.
OL,15,FHowever, she added, the Party can't
OL,16,Fmake further commitments on defence
OL,17,Fspending until after an election.
