OL,3,CGrant Shapps refuses to commit to 3%
OL,4,Cdefence spending in election manifesto
OL,6,F"We will want to conduct a proper
OL,7,Fstrategic defence review if we are in
OL,8,FGovernment to make sure we are
OL,9,Fspending British taxpayers' money as
OL,10,Feffectively as possible."
OL,12,FThe Labour Party also stresses it was
OL,13,Fspending 2.5% of GDP on defence when
OL,14,Fit left office in 2010.
